      <title>2023-02-08 改变 React Component Props 类型定义的习惯</title>
      <link>https://thaddeusjiang.com/2023-02-08-gai-bian-react-component-props-lei-xing-ding-yi-de-xi-guan</link>
			<description><![CDATA[
<div class="container">
    <div class="column is-6-desktop is-offset-3-desktop is-8 is-offset-2 my-4">
      <nav aria-label="main navigation" class="navbar" role="navigation">
